high_descs: Head towards to the sidetable
Take a butter knife in
Head towards to the table
Take a bread in
Keep the butter knife on the side table
Take a bread in
Head towards to the microwave
Keep the bread inside the microwave
Head towards to the garbage can
Put the bread inside the garbage can
anns.task_desc: Put the bread inside the garbage can

high_descs: Go left, out from the room, continue straight and then to the sidetable to your left.
Take a butterknife from the table.
Lean over the bread on the table.
Cut the bread loaf with the cutter.
Put the butterknife back on the sidetable.
Take a piece of bread from the table.
Turn around and proceed to the microwave on your left.
Put the bread in the microwave, heat it up for a while, then take it out.
Move near the entrance to the room you came from, and face the garbagecan on the right.
Put the bread on the garbagecan.
anns.task_desc: Cut the bread and take a piece of it to the GarbageCan

high_descs: Walk straight into the sidetable.
Turn left and take the butterknife from the round table.
Get ready to cut the bread.
Cut the bread into slices.
Keep the butterknife on the sidetable.
Take a slice of bread.
Turn around and walk towards left and go in front of the microwave.
Open the door of the oven and put the bread slice into it and then close the door. Wait for some minutes to make the bread heat and then open the oven and take out the bread slice from it.
Turn to the garbagecan and walk straight and then take a right turn.
Move towards the garbagecan and put the bread slice on the couch.
anns.task_desc: Put the bread slice on the GarbageCan
